  "1867240": {
    "name": "WARDOGS",
    "steam_appid": 1867240,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/e8010a4eac8edf99d05dc0119f6526d4.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/8cafb56052c6ece0ae621691da1618a2.poster.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/8cafb56052c6ece0ae621691da1618a2.webm?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/8cafb56052c6ece0ae621691da1618a2.mp4?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《WARDOGS》是一款全面战争式第一人称射击游戏，在一个最高可支持 100 名玩家的大规模军事沙盒中，融合了战术枪战、诸兵种联合作战以及建造与破坏机制等元素。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏模式灵感源自《山丘之王》，三支队伍将在一张 256 平方公里的地图上，为一块随机生成的 2x2 公里“控制区”的占领权展开争夺。控制区内拥有最多玩家的队伍将获得积分，率先累积至 100 分的队伍将赢得比赛。控制区位置的随机变化，加上每名玩家各不相同的战术选择，使得每一场比赛都独一无二。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/f5c5403a896b0a910d3708e758d63a7d.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/679151b2e8ee7d9018bc555ff81313b7.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/aac5f1f0782c612c0c0b1763cae54253.poster.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/aac5f1f0782c612c0c0b1763cae54253.webm?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/aac5f1f0782c612c0c0b1763cae54253.mp4?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《WARDOGS》中，每一个决定都至关重要。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每名玩家在开始《WARDOGS》之旅时都会有 10000 美元作为初始资金。在每一条生命中，你都需要从种类丰富的武器、装备和载具中进行选择，购买并构建专属配置，为你的队伍赢得胜利提供有力支援。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是复活队友、把友军送到控制区，还是控制目标点，你的每一次团队协作行为都会获得现金奖励。我们不仅仅鼓励团队合作，更以现金予以奖励。玩家可自由选择游戏方式、赚取现金的方式，以及如何使用自己赚取的现金。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局比赛获得的现金将会保留，因此在合适的时机进行大额投资，购买更好的装备或载具，有机会扭转战局，并带来可观的回报。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/f5c5403a896b0a910d3708e758d63a7d.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/5fb2aa02ee2a1f0b6380d6c44daa72bb.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/e759726c4923cbd8e2edaba524ee7ee7.poster.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/e759726c4923cbd8e2edaba524ee7ee7.webm?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/e759726c4923cbd8e2edaba524ee7ee7.mp4?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>怎么玩、怎么赚钱，完全由你决定。</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《WARDOGS》中，没有唯一的玩法、赚钱方式或成长路线。游戏赋予玩家充分的自由，让你可以用各种方式来夺取控制区。无论是当个帮助队伍取胜的独狼玩家，还是加入一支高度协同的小队，如何应战完全由你自己决定。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以追逐“热点区域”来赚取双倍现金，购买吉利服进行远距离狙击，或者驾驶直升机为队友运送补给。你也可以选择修建前沿作战基地，在关键战略要道上构筑防线。又或者，如果你想大肆破坏一番……不妨驾驭火炮坦克，向敌人倾泻毁灭性的火力。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《WARDOGS》中，没有固定的交战规则。你想如何应战，完全取决于你自己。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/f5c5403a896b0a910d3708e758d63a7d.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/6c127b8a76d705e9e21dd0fbfe69bd16.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/320bf18346e688eecd7c867786a53c0e.poster.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/320bf18346e688eecd7c867786a53c0e.webm?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/320bf18346e688eecd7c867786a53c0e.mp4?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战术作战中制造混乱。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用火箭筒摧毁公寓楼，或者驾驶重装甲坦克在城镇中碾压开路。你所到之处，你周围的世界都会作出反应。反过来，你也可以与队友们协同制定战略，在地图上的关键位置加固阵地和筑防，以获得战术优势。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/f5c5403a896b0a910d3708e758d63a7d.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/526aed040011d95a12a5c7835e05e1ae.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1560 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/84d320e9a5fe43524c39cd7d30d8ceb8.poster.avif?t=1770920969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/84d320e9a5fe43524c39cd7d30d8ceb8.webm?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1867240/extras/84d320e9a5fe43524c39cd7d30d8ceb8.mp4?t=1770920969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《WARDOGS》中，每一个瞬间都 100% 是由玩家驱动，并通过本地语音串联，你既可以与队友交流战术，也可以嘲讽敌对玩家。这不是又一款“大逃杀游戏”，也不是又一款“撤离射击游戏”。《WARDOGS》是对全面战争式第一人称射击游戏的一种全新战术化诠释。它奖励理性的决策、有效的沟通和真正的团队协作，并让你在现代军事的背景下，以自己的方式进行游戏。 </p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 繁体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
